1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
The 45-second habit that
doubled my afternoon focus.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:06,000
I used to lose every afternoon. 2
PM hit and my brain was gone.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:16,000
I started doing a 45-second check-in with myself. "How's my energy? What
did I do this morning?" Just awareness — no action needed.

4
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Set a reminder at 2 PM. Rate your energy
1-10. After 7 days you'll know your pattern.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:28,000
I built an app that does this
check-in for you. Free. 30 seconds.

